title: Aubame-out?
description:
The FC crew discuss Pierre-Emerick Aubameyang role with Barcelona now that Robert Lewandowski has signed. Also, Darwin Nunez scoring 4 goals against RB Leipzig and what it means for the rest of the Premier League. Plus, Sadio Mane winning CAF Player of the Year over Mo Salah.
